The main firmware sketch is: boardcaster

This is the integration sketch for code targeted for flash onto the final product and demos.

See the file config.h in boardcaster/ for configuration settings.
	
==Build==
make
		
==Upload (Target: atmega328)==
make upload
		
==Target Change==
Edit Makefile and change TARGET to one of the following:
	
atmega328
mega2560
uno

